Save the file in name-app.py
Run this in Terminal:
pip install streamlit transformers PyPDF2 python-docx reportlab torch

If you face a torch installation issue-
For some systems:
pip install torch --extra-index-url https://download.pytorch.org/whl/cu121

For CPU version:
pip install torch --index-url https://download.pytorch.org/whl/cpu

After installation â€” Run your app-
streamlit run app.py

